# Pong game
# Can be configured as either 1- or 2-player based on the 5th bit of GPIO-A
# GPIO-A usage:
#   0. Player 0 move left
#   1. Player 0 move right
#   2. Player 1 move left
#   3. Player 1 move right
#   4. Player 1 enable
#   4. Start/Reset


# --------------------------------- <Functions> ---------------------------------
@anchor(draw-paddle);
# Pops 2 bytes
# Stack: Paddle position, player number

